  * ''[[manual:api:reference:maintenance:delete|maintenance.delete]]'' - deleting maintenances
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:maintenance:get|maintenance.get]]'' - retrieving maintenances
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:maintenance:update|maintenance.update]]'' - updating maintenances